it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std

Class SignatureBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.SignatureBuilder<Control>
      • it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std.SignatureBuilder

  • public class SignatureBuilder
extends SignatureBuilder<Control>
    The class provides methods for signature construction since Signature is immutable. Every instance of the class maintains a collection of instances of Control which are used to instantiate signatures on demand.
